snippet.title: Eonica Chess Battle - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the world premiere of Eonica Chess Battle. Crowns will fall and new rulers will rise.

SUBSCRIBE to our Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCc6Xn45gUKWBsRfdA3jLnrw/

Follow Eonica Chess Battle:
WEBSITE: https://www.playeonica.com/
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/PlayEonica
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/PlayEonica
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/PlayEonica

About StandArts:
We are fresh game developers and this is our first product. We liked a lot an idea of auto-battlers back in February 2019 and decided to try ourselves in the game industry. With a huge development experience behind our backs and help from the most creative art director we want to make the most interesting games on the market and be a part of this great community. We want to hear your voice and make changes happen.
